<text id="02-output-contract" title="Python Async Patterns — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying python-async. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['uses_taskgroup_for_fanout', 'asyncio_timeout_used', 'semaphore_for_caps', 'no_blocking_call_in_coroutine'],
  "properties": {
    "uses_taskgroup_for_fanout": { "type": "boolean" },
    "asyncio_timeout_used": { "type": "boolean" },
    "semaphore_for_caps": { "type": "boolean" },
    "no_blocking_call_in_coroutine": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>uses_taskgroup_for_fanout</item>
      <item>asyncio_timeout_used</item>
      <item>semaphore_for_caps</item>
      <item>no_blocking_call_in_coroutine</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "uses_taskgroup_for_fanout": true,
  "asyncio_timeout_used": true,
  "semaphore_for_caps": true,
  "no_blocking_call_in_coroutine": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "uses_taskgroup_for_fanout": false,
  "asyncio_timeout_used": false,
  "semaphore_for_caps": false,
  "no_blocking_call_in_coroutine": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-taskgroup-over-gather).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
